FAS ligand expression in inflammatory infiltrate lymphoid cells as a prognostic 
marker in oral squamous cell carcinoma.

Peterle GT(1), Santos M(2), Mendes SO(1), Carvalho-Neto PB(3), Maia LL(1), Stur 
E(1), Agostini LP(1), Silva CV(1), Trivilin LO(1), Nunes FD(4), Carvalho MB(3), 
