Scapular Notching on Kinematic Simulated Range of Motion After Reverse Shoulder 
Arthroplasty Is Not the Result of Impingement in Adduction.

Lädermann A(1), Gueorguiev B, Charbonnier C, Stimec BV, Fasel JHD, Zderic I, 
Hagen J, Walch G.

Author information:
(1)From the Division of Orthopaedics and Trauma Surgery, La Tour Hospital, 
Meyrin (AL); Faculty of Medicine, University of Geneva (AL); Division of 
Orthopaedics and Trauma Surgery, Department of Surgery, Geneva University 
